[DhtmlXQ_open]D36 中炮进三兵对左炮封车转列炮[/DhtmlXQ_open]
[DhtmlXQ_remark]阎文清，张强[/DhtmlXQ_remark]
[DhtmlXQ_author]陈勇[/DhtmlXQ_author]
